# Anomalous nested-path pollution guard
# Prior sessions occasionally resolved absolute paths like
# /home/mac/HA/implementation_10/X against the repo root rather than
# filesystem root, producing /home/mac/HA/implementation_10/home/mac/HA/...
# This guard prevents that pollution from being re-tracked.
# See docs/oal_inbox_merge_to_main_plan_2026_05_05.md §3.2.1 for context.
/home/

